data.meta_description: Serving up the hottest dance, hip hop, and club mixes and DJ remixes.

Cultural Vibe – Ma Foom Bey (Michael Gray Remix)

Michael Gray is a DJ and house music producer from the UK. He is also half of an English house music duo Full Intention. His megamix “The Brits 1990 (Dance Medley)” for the 1990 Brit Awards ceremony reached number two in the UK Singles Chart. His 2004 Read more...

Baauer – AETHER (Hex Cougar Remix)

Hex Cougar is an American electronic music producer and remixer. His most popular original tracks are “Afterlife”, “Sweet Dreams”, “anythingUwant”, “Sex U”, and others. The producer has reworked such artists as Alison Wonderland, Illenium, KRANE, Sia, and others. He has gained support from such respected DJs and Read more...

Lushington – You Got Me Baby (Cat Dealers Remix)

Cat Dealers is an electronic music duo from Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. The musicians have released numerous original singles and remixed big artists, such as R3HAB, Sam Feldt, Cleo, Vintage Culture, to name a few.

Another rework from Cat Dealers is right on point. This time, the producers Read more...

Slow Magic – Home (Covex Remix)

Brendan Bell, best known by his stage name Covex, is an American DJ and electronic music producer from Denver, Colorado. His repertoire includes original compositions as well as remixes for the likes of Hayden James, Gryffin, Petit Biscuit, Hermitude, and many others.

Covex serves up his interpretation of Read more...

Faithless – I Need Someone (Yotto Remix)

Yotto is a record producer, DJ, and songwriter from Finland. In 2018, he released his debut album, Hyperfall. His repertoire also includes numerous singles, five EPs, and remixes for the likes of Diplo, Gorillaz, Coldplay, Pierce Fulton, and many others. Yotto has worked with such prominent artists Read more...

Silk City x Ellie Goulding – New Love (Shane Codd Remix)

Shane Codd is a DJ and EDM producer from Ireland. In 2020, he released his debut single, “Get Out My Head”, which took number five on the Irish Singles Chart and number six on the UK Singles Chart. The same year, Codd reached the top spot on Read more...

Jubel – Weekend Vibe (Kokiri Remix)

Kevin Williams, best known under his stage name Kokiri, is an English electronic music producer and remixer. In 2015, the artist released his breakthrough single “Turn Back Time (Retrospect)” on Ministry of Sound in the UK and on Big Beat/Atlantic in the US. He has also had Read more...

Ava Max – My Head x My Heart (Claptone Remix)

Claptone is a house music duo from Germany. These are quite mysterious artists as they wear golden mask with a beak to hide their identity. Rumors say that they perform at two venues at once, and the sets they play are identical. According to Mixmag, Claptone is Read more...

Doja Cat – Streets (Disclosure Remix)

Disclosure is a British electronic music duo made up of brothers Howard and Guy Lawrence. Their debut album, Settle, was nominated for Best Dance/Electronica Album at the 2014 Grammy Awards. Their second studio album, Caracal, was nominated for Best Dance/Electronica Album at the 2016 Grammy Awards. Their third Read more...

Vintage Culture – Varias Queixas (Vintage Culture x KVSH Remix)

Vintage Culture is a Brazilian electronic music producer and DJ. In 2015, the producer took number 2 on the list of the best Brazilian DJs House Mag. In 2018, he took number 19 in DJ Mag’s Top 100 DJs list.
